OL,3,CMost parents regret giving children a
OL,4,Csmartphone - is it time for a ban?
OL,6,FMost parents regret giving their
OL,7,Fchildren a smartphone and and almost
OL,8,Fhalf believe the devices have changed
OL,9,Ftheir personalities - so is it time
OL,10,Ffor Labour to rethink its policy on
OL,11,Fwhat tech is safe for under 16s?
OL,13,FThe previous government, which banned
OL,14,Fsmartphones from schools, was
OL,15,Fconsidering a ban on selling them to
OL,16,Funder 16s, but new Prime Minister Keir
OL,17,FStarmer has previously dismissed the
OL,18,Fidea as impractical.
