OL,3,CMost parents regret giving children a
OL,4,Csmartphone - is it time for a ban?
OL,6,FThe survey of 10,000 parents in the
OL,7,FUK, US, India, Germany and Australia
OL,8,Falso found that almost 75% fear
OL,9,Fsmartphones expose their children to
OL,10,Finternet dangers.
OL,12,FSeparate research by the Education
OL,13,FSelect Committee from earlier this
OL,14,Fyear also found that children are
OL,15,Fexposed to "serious dangers" online
OL,16,Fand the risks of smartphone usage
OL,17,Foutweigh the benefits.
OL,19,FThe committee said the next government
OL,20,Fshould urgently consider banning
OL,21,Fsmartphones for school-aged children.
