OL,6,FHMD's global survey also found that a
OL,7,Fthird of parents have cried over their
OL,8,Fchild's phone obsession and 55% say it
OL,9,Fis a big source of household arguments.
OL,11,FIt is not yet clear whether Labour
OL,12,Fwill bring in any new legislation to
OL,13,Fresolve the issue, but Dr Becky
OL,14,FFoljambe, founder of Health
OL,15,FProfessionals for Safer Screens, said
OL,16,Fthe research shows "solutions are
OL,17,Furgently needed".
