OL,6,FBut, speaking on LBC days after
OL,7,Fwinning the election, Starmer said:
OL,8,F"In relation to simply banning phones
OL,9,Ffor under 16s, I don't think that's a
OL,10,Fgood idea. I don't think that's a
OL,11,Fpractical way forward.
OL,13,F"But I do think I will sit down with
OL,14,Fanyone to look at how we'll put in
OL,15,Fplace better protections because all
OL,16,Fparents and everybody across the
OL,17,Fcountry is concerned about what can
OL,18,Factually be accessed on a phone."
