OL,6,FCalls for tighter restrictions on
OL,7,Fsmartphones have grown louder amid a
OL,8,Fcampaign by Esther Ghey, the mother of
OL,9,Fmurdered trans teenager Brianna, who
OL,10,Fhas been calling for restrictions on
OL,11,Funder-16s using smartphones and social
OL,12,Fmedia.
OL,14,FShe told BBC Breakfast that at the
OL,15,Fvery least, mobile phone companies
OL,16,Fshould "take more responsibility" over
OL,17,Fthe impact of their products - and Dr
OL,18,FFoljambe agrees.
