OL,6,FDr Foljambe, from Health Professionals
OL,7,Ffor Safer Screens - a group dedicated
OL,8,Fto health and social care
OL,9,Fprofessionals who share concerns about
OL,10,Fthe harmful impact of smartphones on
OL,11,Fchildren - said the "reality is the
OL,12,Ftechnology to protect these children
OL,13,Fcould be improved".
OL,15,FHMD, which owns Nokia, is co-creating
OL,16,Fa new phone with parents to tackle the
OL,17,Fimpact of smartphone use and social
OL,18,Fmedia on the wellbeing of children and
OL,19,Fcreate the choice needed to find
OL,20,Fbalance.
