OL,6,FIt said the Better Phone Project will
OL,7,F"offer a suite of new and innovative
OL,8,Fsolutions which could work for
OL,9,Fparents, their children and anyone who
OL,10,Fis looking for credible alternatives
OL,11,Fto a smartphone".
OL,13,FAlison Winsborough, an assistant
OL,14,Fprincipal at a school in Dorset, said
OL,15,Fparents should have more control over
OL,16,Fhow much children use phones, and even
OL,17,Fher 12-year-old daughter Edie admitted
OL,18,Fher life revolves around her phone.
