OL,6,F"I do spend more time on my phone
OL,7,Fduring the school holidays and I can
OL,8,Fbe on it for hours, scrolling on
OL,9,FTikTok, messaging," Edie said.
OL,11,F"My life does revolve around my
OL,12,Fsmartphone: when I'm doing something
OL,13,Fit's always there and when I'm not
OL,14,Fdoing anything, it's always there.
OL,16,F"Without a smartphone I would have
OL,17,Fmore freedom in the sense that I could
OL,18,Fgo out and enjoy yourself and not take
OL,19,Fpictures and just be with one person
OL,20,Fwithout messaging multiple other
OL,21,Fpeople."
