OL,6,FResponding to the survey, a government
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Creating a safer
OL,8,Fonline world is a priority and
OL,9,Fensuring the Online Safety Act is
OL,10,Fimplemented is an important part of
OL,11,Fthis work.
OL,13,F"Ofcom has set out the steps companies
OL,14,Fwill have to take to protect children
OL,15,Fon their platforms under the Online
OL,16,FSafety Act, including using highly
OL,17,Feffective age checks and altering
OL,18,Ftheir algorithms to filter out harmful
OL,19,Fcontent."
